  "author": "Guru Bin",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "Pressure Drop filtered to near-sub range, reverb damped to remove all air. What dub becomes when it sinks below the surface — the echo still happens, but muffled, slowed, as though the water has changed the physics of the room.",
